channel.title: Won't let me register server on status page
channel.description:
When i put it the status of everything, it says you can only post one server, but i haven't posted one in over 3 months. I cleared my cache and all the other crap and stuff like that, forwarded ports.
I never had a problem with the status page when posting before..
